    "title": "Allcargo Logistics is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "Join the Allcargo Logistics family as a Warehouse Manager in Coimbatore. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Allcargo Logistics:\nAllcargo Logistics is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Allcargo Logistics!",
